# Digital Transformation Framework

**Four strategic pillars for transformation:**

<<mermaid>>
  flowchart TB
      A[Digital Transformation Strategy] --> B[Customer Experience]
      A --> C[Operational Excellence]
      A --> D[Data & Analytics]
      A --> E[Technology Infrastructure]
      
      B --> F["Omnichannel Platform<br/>Mobile-first Design<br/>Self-service Portal"]
      C --> G["Process Automation<br/>AI-powered Operations<br/>Digital Workflows"]
      D --> H["Real-time Analytics<br/>Predictive Insights<br/>Customer Intelligence"]
      E --> I["Cloud Migration<br/>API Architecture<br/>Security Framework"]
      
      style A fill:#1976d2,color:#fff
      style B fill:#4caf50,color:#fff
      style C fill:#ff9800,color:#fff
      style D fill:#9c27b0,color:#fff
      style E fill:#f44336,color:#fff

**Integrated approach ensures maximum impact**

@notes:
- Four pillars work together synergistically
- Customer experience drives revenue growth
- Operations excellence reduces costs
- Data enables intelligent decision making
- Technology provides foundation for all

