# Customer Experience Transformation

**Creating digital-first customer journeys**

::: info
**Priority Initiatives:**
- **Omnichannel Platform:** Unified experience across all touchpoints
- **Mobile App:** Native iOS/Android with full functionality
- **Self-Service Portal:** 80% of inquiries resolved without agent
- **Personalization Engine:** AI-driven content and recommendations
:::

**Target: 95% customer satisfaction by end of Year 1**

@notes:
- Omnichannel most requested feature from customers
- Mobile app will capture younger demographics
- Self-service reduces costs while improving satisfaction
- Personalization drives engagement and loyalty

---

