**Streamlining processes with intelligent automation**

| Process Area | Current State | Target State | Efficiency Gain |
|--------------|---------------|--------------|-----------------|
| **Order Processing** | 4.2 hours | 45 minutes | 82% faster |
| **Customer Onboarding** | 12 days | 3 days | 75% faster |
| **Compliance Reporting** | 40 hours/month | 8 hours/month | 80% reduction |
| **Quality Assurance** | Manual checks | AI-powered | 60% cost reduction |

**Total operational savings: $12M annually**

@notes:
- Process improvements based on pilot programs
- Order processing automation already tested
- Onboarding improvements customer-validated
- Savings calculations reviewed by finance team

