# Implementation Timeline

**{{transformation_timeline}} phased rollout:**

| Phase | Duration | Key Deliverables | Investment |
|-------|----------|------------------|------------|
| **Phase 1** | Months 1-6 | Cloud foundation, Customer portal | $15M |
| **Phase 2** | Months 7-12 | Mobile app, Process automation | $18M |
| **Phase 3** | Months 13-18 | Analytics platform, AI capabilities | $12M |
| **Phase 4** | Months 19-24 | Full integration, Optimization | $8M |

**Total investment: {{digital_budget}} over {{transformation_timeline}}**

@notes:
- Front-loaded investment for faster ROI
- Each phase builds on previous achievements
- Customer-facing improvements prioritized
- Phase 4 focuses on optimization and refinement

